  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective, randomized control trial will use passive, isocapnic hyperventilation,
      applied via the ClearMateTM device (Thornhill Medical, Inc) versus controls receiving
      standard of care supportive management for severe alcohol intoxication to assess for enhanced
      ethanol elimination kinetics.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
